Data Sources
------------
This database was compiled from primary research (surveys and interviews)
conducted between 2022 and 2025, as well as the following secondary sources:

1. Universidad Internacional de La Rioja (UNIR) — Institutional research data
   License: Used with institutional permission

2. Survey data collected from university students and researchers across
   Argentina, Brazil, Chile, Colombia, Mexico, and Peru (2022-2025).
   Participants provided informed consent per ethical protocols.

3. Published literature on AI adoption in higher education (for validation)
   — Individual papers cited in the dataset documentation.

Ethical Compliance
------------------
All primary data was collected under ethical approval and informed consent.
Personal identifiers have been removed. The dataset is fully anonymized.

